antipodiana 
<authority id="45983E6120379284AC68F2BF6968E138" pageId="5" pageNumber="109">Forster</authority>
</taxonomicName>
, 1955,Ree. Dominion Mus., 2: 198, Figs. 52-55,?,from Antipodes Island is a 
<taxonomicName id="84B865D212937B8B79F17F30CB1723DE" class="Arachnida" family="Theridiidae" genus="Pholcomma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pholcomma</taxonomicName>
, Marples, Ree. Auckland Inst. Mus. (in press) describes a new genus from New Zealand whose 
<typeStatus id="43E24D67CCAC731F584D9E739D8F6A74">type</typeStatus>
species is quite close to 
<taxonomicName id="898ED39A48921E6EE28BD287C4029250" class="Arachnida" family="Theridiidae" genus="Pholcomma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsuta">Pholcomma hirsuta</taxonomicName>
